body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/597\n\nThe 2026.7.18 CLI returns changed_fields: [] for an empty append but still rewrites updated_at. Align append with the nonblank annotation/title contracts and protect false-freshness semantics. Duplicate check searched all statuses for append, empty/whitespace text, no-op, and updated_at freshness. Closed pm-7je0, pm-45mb, and pm-zwpp are related validation/mutation lineages but do not cover append freshness."
